# Figma Learning Notes 🎨

## What is Figma?
Figma is a cloud-based UI/UX design tool used to design:
- Mobile Apps
- Websites
- Dashboards
- Prototypes
- User Interfaces

It allows designers and developers to collaborate in real time.

